                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2862" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0667</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8312 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">落地何其难——投资控股型企业的产业投资组合配置之惑</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How to Implement the Strategy—The Confusion of Investment Portfolio Allocation of Investment Holding Enterprises</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵杨，张秋生</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天海丰收控股集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">投资控股型公司；产业投资价值评估；产业投资方向遴选；产业投资组合配置</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">reform of China’s state-owned companies; investment-holding companies; investment evaluation system of industries；selection of the industry investment；Investment Portfolio Allocation of industries</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例以党的十八届三中全会后我国国企改革为大背景，描写大型国有企业——丰收集团响应国家组建国有资本投资运营公司的改革方向，意欲在“十三五”期间构建投资控股型战略，实现从“管资产”到“管资本”的转变。然而，在此过程中，集团总部高管层一直困扰于以下问题：一、作为投资控股型企业而言，如何通过建立一套科学、客观、可操作性强的产业投资评估体系来统一测定既有的与拟涉足产业的投资价值？二、如何基于集团自身所具备的能力与资源在投资价值较高的产业中遴选出未来要投资的产业方向？三、如何在所形成的分属不同产业的投资项目组合中合理地配置资源，以达成科学合理的产业梯次与各项目间较强的协同效应，最终实现整体上资本收益与风险的平衡？本案例启发学生对投资控股型公司战略规划中比较独特的产业投资组合配置方案这个核心问题进行深入思考，并尝试提出切实可行的解决之道。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the end of the Third Plenary Session of the 18th Central Committee of CPC, the new reform of state-owned companies (SOEs) in China has begun. To explore a correct strategy position of the development, this case analyzes the reform process of FengShou Group. In order to seize the historic opportunity of SOE reform, FengShou Group want to establish “investment-holding” strategic during the period of “13th Five-Year” so as to shift the focus of enterprise management from &quot;assets&quot; to &quot;capital&quot;. In this process, however, the senior management of Group headquarters has been trapped in the following issues: First of all, as an investment-holding companies how to set up a scientific, objective and strong operability of industry investment evaluation system which can be used to determine the investment value of existing and planned to be involved in the industry? Secondly, how to select the future investment direction among industry of high investment value based on the group’s ability and resources? Thirdly, how to reasonably allocating resources to the different investment portfolio which belongs to disparate industries to achieve a scientific and reasonable industrial grads and strong synergies between various projects, finally, realizes the balance between capital gains and risk? Along with the successive release of the top-level design plan of the reform of SOEs—“Guiding Opinions on Deepening the Reform of SOEs” and its supporting documents, we can find that transformation and upgrading as state-owned investment holding company is one of the direction of the reform of enterprise groups. Generally speaking, these enterprise groups whose management involved in many mixed industries are large state-owned enterprise groups of our country. This case can inspire the student to carry on the comprehensive thinking on the uniqueness of strategic planning of investment holding company, at the same time, we can encourage students to put forward a practical solution to the core problem of the unique industrial portfolio allocation strategy.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《产业经济学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">产业投资组合的合理配置、投资价值评估模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017-09</td>
                            </tr>
